      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic order. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014addressing the critical weak points of the chassis. It retains its factory-spec limited-slip differential and original suspension geometry for an authentic M-division driving experience. The exterior finish is exceptional, with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. A turnkey, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
